name: GoFit
0:
”Alexa, open go fit.”
”Give me a 10 minutes easy workout.”
”Alexa, ask go fit to give me a 5 minutes hard workout.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: go fit
des:
Go Fit is a flexible workout skill that allows you to specify the duration and difficulty of your workout.

Ask Go Fit for an easy, medium, or hard workout depending on how you feel that day. Tell Go Fit how long you want to workout. Go Fit's flexibility allows you to sneak in a workout even on a busy day!

Disclaimer: The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only.

Please send any suggestions, questions, and bug reports to @jpufffff on twitter. All feedback is appreciated and will help me improve this skill for everyone.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
